石綿定唔知乜野有害材料而家唔比用先唔洗拆<br />\n佢同我講佢屋企後面有人成間舊拆左起左棟新三層村屋<br />\n最後都要成棟拆哂而家一塊爛地"},{"pid":"70b054458fefebb189cb770f42f023fae148806a","tid":2294411,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"寮屋重建好難，要申請用返相同物料，唔可以起大"},{"pid":"e4063f2ed53acb8806f21912c71bc9ddbc0085c8","tid":2294411,"uid":55573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCApPD2-8-k&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcCApPD2-8-k%26t%3D1s&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM35IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=7d06edd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCApPD2-8-k&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n但係牌照屋咁改 就可以?"},{"pid":"8936630b119dbcd512cf92bc9b121dde5600a449","tid":2294411,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4063f2ed53acb8806f21912c71bc9ddbc0085c8","tid":2294411,"uid":55573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCApPD2-8-k&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcCApPD2-8-k%26t%3D1s&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM35IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=7d06edd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCApPD2-8-k&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n但係牌照屋咁改 就可以?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"一樣，叫法唔同。牌照屋又叫紅字屋，你屋出面牆係咪用紅色寫上左number丫<br />\n呢間野係偷雞的，仲要搭埋出去。<br />\n地政唔捉係一件事，想偷雞則則膊就睇你敢唔敢"},{"pid":"648686408bcf5d3838c0ad9f026d0216819c94ca","tid":2294411,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"個個都偷雞起，邊個真係會入紙申請"},{"pid":"29d1f243b3037aef100d1f98a9b3f61d4852a609","tid":2294411,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"我住果條村d人通常搭上搭咁搵d大陸人黎做"},{"pid":"293da104c891f852da30a7ebc7a954dc56c209aa","tid":2294411,"uid":55573,"like":0,"dis